 <summary>WatchFlower is a plant monitoring application that reads and plots data from your Xiaomi / MiJia 'Flower Care' and 'Ropot' devices!</summary>
 <description>
  <p>
   WatchFlower is a plant monitoring application that reads and plots data from your Xiaomi MiJia "Flower Care" and "Ropot" Bluetooth sensors.
   WatchFlower also works great with a couple of Bluetooth thermometers!
  </p>
